description: Last year, Colonel Sanders battled his evil twin from Earth-3 in the instant classic The Colonel of Two Worlds. Now the Anti-Colonel is attacking the Multiverse, and the future of fried chicken lies with Colonels from various worlds spanning the Multiverse! Don't miss the strangest, funniest, most epic adventure ever. It's Colonel Quality Guaranteed!
